2d:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"MChJ kalkulyatori O'zbekistondagi tadbirkorlarga turli soliqqa tortish tizimlarida soliq yukini hisoblashga yordam beradi. Mas'uliyati cheklangan jamiyat (MChJ) — mamlakatda biznes yuritishning eng keng tarqalgan shakli. Soliq kodeksiga ko'ra, MChJ umumiy tizimda (foyda solig'i 15% + "}],"$L34",["$","$1","2",{"children":" 12%) yoki soddalashtilgan tizimda (xarajatlarni chegirmasdan aylanma solig'i 4%) ishlashi mumkin."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Umumiy soliqqa tortish tizimida MChJ quyidagilarni to'laydi: foyda solig'i — sof foydaning 15% (daromadlar minus hujjat bilan tasdiqlangan xarajatlar); "}],"$L35",["$","$1","2",{"children":" — aylanma 60 000 "}],"$L36",["$","$1","4",{"children":" (taxminan 24,72 mlrd so'm) dan oshganda 12%; ijtimoiy soliq — ish haqi fondining 12%; "}],"$L37",["$","$1","6",{"children":" — xodimlar ish haqidan 12% (ish haqidan ushlab qolinadi). Ta'sischilar dividendlari 5% stavkada JShShSga tortiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Tizimlar o'rtasidagi tanlov tushumdagi xarajatlar ulushiga bog'liq. Agar xarajatlar tushumning 60% dan ortiq bo'lsa, umumiy tizim foydaliroq — siz faqat farqning 15% ini to'laysiz. Xarajatlar 40% dan kam bo'lsa, soddalashtilgan tizim (aylanmaning 4%) arzonroq. Kalkulyatorimiz prognoz daromadlar va xarajatlarni kiritish va qaysi tizim biznesingiz uchun optimal ekanligini bir zumda ko'rish imkonini beradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda MChJni ro'yxatdan o'tkazish my.gov.uz portali orqali amalga oshiriladi va 1–3 ish kunini oladi. Minimal ustav kapitali belgilanmagan. Ro'yxatdan o'tkazish uchun davlat boji — taxminan 1 "}],"$L38",["$","$1","2",{"children":" (412 000 so'm). Ro'yxatdan o'tganidan keyin bankda hisob-kitob raqamini ochish, my.soliq.uz orqali soliq organlarida ro'yxatdan o'tish va hisobot topshirish uchun elektron raqamli imzoni olish kerak."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Bizning MChJ kalkulyatorimiz ikkala tizim uchun to'liq soliq yukini hisoblaydi: kutilayotgan tushum, xarajatlar, ish haqi fondi va xodimlar sonini kiriting — barcha soliqlarning batafsil hisobi va optimal tizim bo'yicha tavsiya oling. Bu boshlang'ich tadbirkorlar va optimallashtirish rejalashtiruvchi amaldagi biznes egalari uchun almastirib bo'lmas vosita."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":"$L39"}]]]}],"$L3a","$L3b"]}]
